<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000972/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Evaluation will assess if students have acquired all the competences of the subject. Thus, evaluation through global assessment will be carried out considering all the evaluation techniques used in progressive evaluation, and will be celebrated in the exam period approved by the Junta de Escuela for the current academic semester and year.

Extraordinary examination will be carried out exclusively by the final global method."""@es ;
